          "_name": "header9",
          "_customHTML": "<section class=\"header9\" group=\"Headers\" data-bg-video=\"{{bg.type == 'video' && bg.value.url}}\" mbr-class=\"{'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n                    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n\n    <mbr-parameters>\n    <!-- Block parameters controls (Blue \"Gear\" panel) -->\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Screen\" name=\"fullScreen\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"9\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"9\" step=\"1\" value=\"4\" condition=\"fullScreen == false\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Arrow\" name=\"showArrow\">\n\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Title\" name=\"showTitle\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Subtitle\" name=\"showSubTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Show Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\">\n\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Background Image\" value=\"@PROJECT_PATH@/assets/images/background1.jpg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Background Color\" value=\"#000000\" selected>\n            <input type=\"video\" title=\"Background Video\" value=\"http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=uNCr7NdOJgw\">\n        </fieldset>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#000000\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.2\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    <!-- End block parameters -->\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type!== 'color'\" mbr-style=\"{'opacity': overlayOpacity, 'background-color': overlayColor}\">\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"media-container-column mbr-white col-md-8\">\n            <h1 class=\"mbr-section-title align-left mbr-bold pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\"><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\">STORY OF A BRAND'S</span><span style=\"font-weight: normal;\"><br></span>BIRTH</h1>\n            <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle align-left mbr-light pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showSubTitle\"><div>—</div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">Project Owners:</span></div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">Etick Pars Intelligent Technologies Development Co.</b><br></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><b>Fanap Payment</b></span></div><div><br></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><b><br></b></span></div><div>—</div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">My Solutions:\n</span></div><div><b style=\"font-style: normal; font-size: 1.2rem;\">Magazine Advertisement</b><br></div><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\"><b>Copywriting</b></span></div><br><br>—<br><div><span style=\"font-style: normal;\">Descriptions:</span></div></h3>\n            <p class=\"mbr-text align-left pb-3 mbr-fonts-style\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\"><b>About Fanap Payment:</b><b><br></b><br>FANAP PAYMENT, a subsidiary of FANAP ICT holding, has been providing different customers with a wide range of payment solutions for more than a decade. Thanks to our young, talented, and highly motivated team, we are known as a leading company in Iran payment industry. Our purpose is to facilitate the purchase process both for merchants and consumers through delivering in-store, mobile and web-based services; merchants receive funds without any concerns or complexity and consumers benefit a fast, easy, and secure payment experience. We dedicate ourselves to enable a world-class seamless payment experience.<br></p>\n            <div class=\"mbr-section-btn align-left\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-4\">\n                <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-primary\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\">LEARN MORE</a>\n                <a class=\"btn btn-md btn-black-outline\" href=\"https://mobirise.com\">LIVE DEMO</a>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div mbr-if=\"showArrow\" class=\"mbr-arrow hidden-sm-down\" aria-hidden=\"true\">\n        <a href=\"#next\">\n            <i class=\"mbri-down mbr-iconfont\"></i>\n        </a>\n    </div>\n</section>",
